column1: "description": "This table gives an overview of commodity-wise capacity at Indian Ports by the end of Twelfth Five Year Plan (2016-17). It gives details regarding the number of existing major ports in 2011-12 and forecasts of number of major ports in 2016-17."
"title": "Download XLS for Commodity-Wise Capacity at Indian Ports by the end of Twelfth Five Year Plan"
